---
title: Turkish-Spiced Chicken & Hummus Wraps with Tomato & Cucumber
description: There’s nothing like a hearty wrap—what’s not to love about our favorite veggies, proteins, and sauces all at the same time in one portable format? This flavorful version stars Turkish-spiced chicken, crisp cucumber, and juicy seasoned tomato wrapped in a warm tortilla spread with creamy, garlicky hummus. It’s a wholesome 10-minute lunch idea you can enjoy at home or, just as easily, take on the road.
